source.name: National Center for Education Statistics (NCES) - Integrated Postsecondary Education Data System (IPEDS) - Awards/degrees Conferred by Program - 2011 - API
source.description: The total number of awards by type of program and level of award (certificate or degree). Type of program is categorized according to the Classification of Instructional Programs (CIP), a detailed coding system for postsecondary instructional programs. Data covers all awards granted between July 1, 2010 and June 30, 2011. This file contains multiple records per institution. Each record is uniquely defined by the variables IPEDS ID (UNITID), classification of instructional program (CIPCODE) and award level (AWLEVEL). Data shown are for first majors only.
